      <title>勒庞与左翼政党争夺权力，法国市场紧张不安</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/france-elections-as-le-pen-rallies-support-markets-brace-for-uncertain-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在极右翼与左翼联盟斗争之际，要求选民选出新议会的选举将让投资者保持警惕。]]></description>
