    <item>
      <title>香港最高法院审理黎智英上诉案 审查日益严格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/hong-kong-top-court-hears-jimmy-lai-appeal-as-scrutiny-mounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一批外国法官相继离职后，香港司法系统再度受到审视，香港最高法院开始首次审理前媒体大亨黎智英在 2019 年支持民主的抗议活动中所扮演的角色的案件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/hong-kong-top-court-hears-jimmy-lai-appeal-as-scrutiny-mounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 02:03:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度议会分裂 莫迪部分议程面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/parts-of-modi-s-agenda-face-risk-in-india-s-fractured-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪的政党十年来首次未能赢得议会绝对多数席位，导致其庞大的国内议程陷入危险，迫使其不得不与多个政党联盟合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/parts-of-modi-s-agenda-face-risk-in-india-s-fractured-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克领导的保守党担心博彩丑闻可能扩大并埋葬他们</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/rishi-sunak-s-tories-fear-betting-scandal-may-expand-and-bury-them</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的执政党保守党难以遏制有关首相数名亲密助手对投票日期进行押注的爆料，他避免在英国大选中遭遇压倒性失败的机会进一步减小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/rishi-sunak-s-tories-fear-betting-scandal-may-expand-and-bury-them</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃姆霍夫称反犹主义使拜登和特朗普的投票“二元化”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/antisemitism-surge-makes-biden-trump-binary-vote-emhoff-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[第二位先生道格·埃姆霍夫表示，重新选举乔·拜登总统对于打击反犹太主义至关重要，并指责唐纳德·特朗普在 2018 年匹兹堡犹太教堂枪击案现场发表讲话后发表评论“煽动仇恨的火焰”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/antisemitism-surge-makes-biden-trump-binary-vote-emhoff-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 20:43:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯达吉斯坦枪手杀害警察和一名牧师</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/six-police-officers-and-a-priest-killed-in-russia-s-dagestan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当局称，枪手袭击了俄罗斯穆斯林聚居区达吉斯坦的教堂和犹太教堂，造成至少 15 名警察和 1 名牧师死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/six-police-officers-and-a-priest-killed-in-russia-s-dagestan</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 18:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>酷热天气致朝觐死亡人数升至 1,300 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-23/over-1-000-pilgrims-died-during-this-year-s-hajj-pilgrimage-in-saudi-arabia-officials-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[开罗（美联社）——沙特当局周日宣布，今年沙特阿拉伯朝觐期间，由于信徒在这个沙漠王国的伊斯兰圣地遭遇极端高温，导致 1,300 多人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-23/over-1-000-pilgrims-died-during-this-year-s-hajj-pilgrimage-in-saudi-arabia-officials-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 08:25:39 GMT</pubDate>
